---
import Button from '@components/Button.astro';
import RadiusGradientFrame from '@components/RadiusGradientFrame.astro';
---

<section>
  <RadiusGradientFrame class="event">
    <div class="event-info">
      <h1>¿QUE ESPERAR DEL EVENTO?</h1>
      <p>
        Tendremos preparadas muchas actividades programadas y un ambiente solo para tí, no
        necesitarás saber inglés, contaremos con intérpretes para que no te pierdas ningún detalle
        de tu expositor favorito
      </p>
      <Button link="/registro" icon="arrow-up-right">Registrarse</Button>
    </div>
    <div class="event-specs">
      <img src="/assets/branch-event.avif" alt="Branch" />
      <ul>
        <li>Workshops dentro del mismo recinto</li>
        <li>Áreas de descanso</li>
        <li>
          Swag bag con temática de la JSConf Chile 2023
          <ul>
            <li><span>Código de la conducta</span></li>
            <li>
              Consideraciones alimenticias (Dependiendo de tus preferencias al momento de comprar la
              entrada)
            </li>
          </ul>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </RadiusGradientFrame>
</section>

<style>
  .event {
    --border-color: linear-gradient(90deg, #2a2401 0%, #9a8025 39.57%, #ede060 100%);
    --border-width: 2px;
    --shadow: 0px 4px 85.3px 0px #55552e1a;
    --radius: 1rem;

    @media (width <= 800px) {
      --shadow: 0px 4px 85.3px rgba(64, 64, 64, 0.1);
      --radius: 0.5rem;
      --border-color: linear-gradient(327.26deg, #ffffff 31.78%, #272727 63.2%, #656565 93.99%);

      background: radial-gradient(95.25% 166.54% at 98.39% 2.85%, #272727 8%, rgba(9, 9, 7, 0) 80%),
        linear-gradient(0.07deg, rgba(64, 64, 64, 0.2) 0.03%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 95.96%);
    }
  }

  .event {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-around;
    height: 28rem;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 71rem;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    box-shadow: 0px 4px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0px 4px 85.3px 0px #55552e1a;
    background:
      linear-gradient(0, var(--bg-color), var(--bg-color)) padding-box,
      var(--gradient-2) border-box;

    @media (width <= 768px) {
      --shadow: 0px 4px 85.3px rgba(64, 64, 64, 0.1);
      --radius: 10px;
      --border-color: linear-gradient(
        90deg,
        #090907 46.45%,
        #1d1b0e 63.08%,
        #413e21 78.39%,
        #aaa255 86.07%
      );

      background:
        linear-gradient(0, var(--bg-color), var(--bg-color)) padding-box,
        var(--gradient-2) border-box;
    }

    & .event-info {
      max-width: 500px;

      & h1 {
        text-wrap: balance;
        line-height: 1.2;
      }

      & p {
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      }
    }

    & .event-specs {
      display: flex;
      max-width: 440px;

      & ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding-left: 0;
        margin-top: 2.5rem;

        & li {
          padding-bottom: 1.8rem;

          & ul {
            padding-top: 2rem;
            padding-left: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 0;

            & span {
              color: var(--yellow);
              font-weight: 600;
              text-decoration: underline;
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }

  @media (width <= 768px) {
    .event {
      flex-direction: column;
      height: 44rem;
      justify-content: space-between;

      & .event-info {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;

        & h1 {
          font-size: 1.25rem;
        }
      }

      & .event-specs {
        & ul {
          margin-bottom: 0;
        }
      }
    }
  }
</style>
